Package: nameparser
Title: GBIF Scientific Name Parser (Rust)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Markus", "Döring", email = "mdoering@gbif.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R binding (via extendr) to the Rust port of the GBIF scientific name
    parser. Parses scientific names into their structured atoms (genus, epithets,
    authorship, rank, etc).
